 About 
 
Letters of Note is an attempt to gather and sort fascinating letters, postcards, telegrams, faxes, and memos. Scans/photos where possible. Fakes will be sneered at. Updated as often as possible; usually each weekday. Learn more here . Edited by  Shaun Usher , who also runs  Lists of Note  &amp;  Letterheady . Contribute/get in touch . Follow Letters of Note... RSS | Email | Twitter Tumblr | Facebook 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
